SELECT Patients.patient_name, Diagnoses.diagnosis, Models.model_name FROM Patients JOIN Diagnoses ON Patients.patient_id = Diagnoses.image_id JOIN Results ON Results.diagnosis_id = Diagnoses.diagnosis_id JOIN Models ON Results.model_id = Models.model_id WHERE Results.result_status = 'positive';

SELECT Patients.patient_name, Images.image_path, Models.model_name, Results.result_status FROM Patients JOIN Images ON Patients.patient_id = Images.patient_id JOIN Diagnoses ON Images.image_id = Diagnoses.image_id JOIN Results ON Diagnoses.diagnosis_id = Results.diagnosis_id JOIN Models ON Results.model_id = Models.model_id WHERE Patients.age < 40 AND Models.trained_on_date > '2021-01-01';

SELECT Patients.patient_name, COUNT(DISTINCT Diagnoses.diagnosis_id) AS `diagnosis_count` FROM Patients JOIN Images ON Patients.patient_id = Images.patient_id JOIN Diagnoses ON Images.image_id = Diagnoses.image_id GROUP BY Patients.patient_name HAVING diagnosis_count > 1;
